subject: Suits and Litigation
Madison Square Garden
Sexual Harassment
lead_paragraph: In a lawsuit filed nearly three years ago, Courtney Prince, the former captain of the Rangers City Skaters, sued the Garden and two of the team’s employees for sexual harassment.
